    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Use to refer to units of luminous flux. It is equal to the amount of flux emitted by one candela into a cone having the solid angle of one steradian.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
